These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
City: new-york, prague
The people have 2 different jobs:  pilot, videographer
2 different games are played: scrabble, chess
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, japanese
1. the japanese is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
2. the person traveling to prague is in an even position##4
3. the videographer is the person traveling to new-york##1
4. the japanese is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| City      | new-york  | prague   |
| Job   | videographer     | pilot   |
| Game         | chess | scrabble |
| Nationality     | brazilian | japanese    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, june
The people have 2 different jobs:  freelancer, software-developer
There are 2 different nationalities: polish, indonesian
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, orchid
1. the indonesian is in an odd position##4
2. the freelancer is the person who growsorchid##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the software-developer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Birthday          | april     | june |
| Job   | software-developer | freelancer  |
| Nationality           | indonesian         | polish     |
| Flower     | azalea   | orchid    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
