2 different games are played: bridge, scrabble
1. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the colombian##3
2. the futuristic house is on the right of the colombian##1
3. the person traveling to venice is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| City    | marseilles     | venice |
| Nationality         | colombian | dutch    |
| House         | craftsman         | futuristic        |
| Game   | bridge         | scrabble    |

