.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, aconite
The people have 2 different jobs:  photographer, journalist
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, rugby
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, azure
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the journalist is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
3. the person who likes azure is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Flower      | aconite     | balloon-flower |
| Job          | journalist   | photographer  |
| Sport         | snowboarding | rugby     |
| Color   | red  | azure         |

