.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
There 2 different types of food: banana, avocado
House: cape-cod, modern
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, mirinda
There are 2 different favourite colors: light-blue, amber
1. the person who likes amber is in an even position##4
2. the modern house is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person eating avocado is the cape-cod house##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Food           | avocado | banana    |
| House   | cape-cod       | modern |
| Beverage           | fanta         | mirinda    |
| Color         | light-blue    | amber   |

