1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Pet      | frog | rat       |
| House          | cape-cod   | victorian    |
| Birthday           | april   | may |
| Game   | domino      | scrabble    |

