2 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, game
1. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
2. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is in an even position##4
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
| Flower           | daffodil | amaryllis |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | fanta      |
| City           | colone      | prague          |
| Cigar         | game | siglo       |

