.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, salsa
There are 2 different favourite colors: coral, black
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, dahlia
2 different games are played: chess, poker
1. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
3. the person playing chess is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Music-Genre    | funk | salsa    |
| Color         | black        | coral |
| Flower         | begonia          | dahlia     |
| Game   | chess        | poker     |

 